Join us as India’s top entrepreneurs share their journeys, secrets, and insights. Learn from their experiences as they reveal the stories behind their business breakthroughs.

That’s a wrap on @therockfordcircle Season 2!! 🎬
We didn’t just tell brand stories - we cracked them open. This season? A no-filter deep dive into what really powers modern Indian brands: sharp pivots, bold moves, messy middles, and a whole lot of magic!

From boardrooms to breakdowns, it’s been a front-row seat to ambition in action. I’ve been your host, your hype squad, and your co-conspirator in curiosity. Until next time - stay curious, stay caffeinated, and we’ll see you back in The Rockford Circle.
